 <metadata>
  <name>RTR - Out and back along the canal</name>
  <desc>An easy out and back route along the canal towards Elton Reservoir. This route avoids the closed section of the banana path. Follow the route at a conversational pace and, when you reach the end, turn around and come back!</desc>
  <author>
   <name>Paul Cox</name>
   <link href="https://www.strava.com/athletes/90628842"/>
  </author>
